decoder

Interface Decoder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DecoderImpl

    public interface Decoder
    This interface is for a prefix code decoder that will take a symbol and it's code and store it. It allows users to input their coding and use it to decode messages.

    • Method Summary
